s G.I. good tastes alike. It seems to me that we're forever getting "C" rations and after a period of time they get somewhat boring. I'm now eating for the sake of nourishment and not the pleasure connected with it."--Company B, 8th Replacement Bn., 1st R
eplacement Depot.
