 complain about. We are getting plenty to eat (I had nine large hot-cakes the other morning) and Uncle Sam is taking pretty good care to see that we get ample smokes, etc. We even are able to buy a few bars of candy a week, and two or three packages of ch
ewing gum, which is plenty for me."--286th Signal Company.
