t are offered by the special services. Special mention is again noted for the excellence of programs offered by the American Radio Station here. The troops in this area appear to be about 95% content with the entertainment available to them. The following
 excerpts have been noted:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16413026 
