\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16413026  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9251421 we have had; everyone enjoyed it very much." --D.T.C. APO 600.
