e
 men in the tent share. The tent is rather crowded but we do have enough room to stand to dress and it is nice to have the things that we need close at hand rather than having to go to another pup tent and rummage in barracks bags for thirty minutes findi
ng everything that you possess before you find the thing that you want. Our furniture is certainly not a work of art however as long as we are comfortable I guess that is the thing of most importance." net.12th Weather Squadron.
