r both the American and German radio programs. News has increased in circulation to the troops in this theater, of conditions in Tunisia. Enemy propaganda is still enjoyed. Apparently the newly arrived officers from the States have not been informed as to
 the war news in this theater. The following remarks have been noted:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16413026 
