"Last night we had to fall out for a night formation to hear a General speak. It's rather rough to fall out day and night but this was really worthwhile. He gave us at least a glimps
e of the good and bad that's happening on the front and any news here is literally eaten up."--Co. B, 8th Bn., 1st Replacement Depot.
