edge of the military events of this war. Most of them believe that French North Africa was entirely occupied by Germany before we landed here in November. It is certainly a sad picture to see that officers arriving in a theater of war don't know what is g
oing on. I suppose too many people are still reading only the funnies and comics"--209th C.A. Regt.
