ast June, 1942 and was effective June 1, 1942. The first $22.00 was taken out of my June earnings. This June 1st will mark the end of one year. I will have had a total of $220.00 deducted from my pay and you haven't received a penny of it. It certainly ca
lls for an explanation and I suggest you do some demanding about that money. Actually you are entit
led to $500.00 counting the money the Government promised to add to my allotment. What you oughter find out is where the hell is the money?" You mentioned a 
