st I have gotten to the Red Cross is to donate two dollars to them a couple of days ago. Maybe the outfits who are stationed in the towns and cities are able to get the entertainment etc that the Red Cross puts out but not us."--8th Troop Carrier Sq., 62n
d Troop Carrier Gp.
