idding aside, glad to have you with me. Glad to welcome you into the American Army-as a fellow soldier in the fight against the forces of Nazism, Fascism, tyranny, and darkness. And I'm sure that wherever you'll be, whatever you'll do, you'll give your be
st to the army, the government and to the people of the United States."--Company B, 6th Bn., 1st Replacement Depot.
