he Jerry noses to some outpost where some of the boys get to losing hopes of ever seeing a woman's smile or hearing one laugh again as pure wishful thinking. Never will you hear any stories of their efforts and those of the 'Y' and other organizations, li
ke came out of the last war. This is really 100% all-American."--Company I1, 47th Infantry.
