s
e, they do not always have the same equipment, and often times are aggressive enough. I have come to the conclusion that we are not a militaristic nation, and that England is. Those soldiers are plenty mean, with a high fighting morale, and a will to go r
i
ght back and give them hell. I think with a few months of seasoning our men will develop too. The German soldier is aces, so all say, everyone has healthy respect for them. We get lots of stories here, direct from the front which probably would be beat to
